  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Sofosbuvir Based Antiviral Regimen for Treating Hepatitis C in Patients With Moderate to Advanced Chronic Kidney Disease and Patients Receiving Renal Replacement Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Study on Safety and Efficacy of Sofosbuvir Based Antiviral Regimen for Treating Hepatitis C in Patients With Moderate to Advanced Chronic Kidney Disease and Patients Receiving Renal Replacement Therapy</official_title>
