  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      All patients with chronic kidney disease (stages 3, 4 and 5) and chronic dialysis patients
      with HCV infection attending nephrology and Hepatology OPD or getting outpatient dialysis at
      the dialysis unit of ILBS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
